frames.caption: A sleek, futuristic UFO hovers outside an airplane window, illuminated by the warm glow of sunset. The craft's smooth metallic surface reflects the soft, golden light, creating a surreal and captivating scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a UFO seen from the window of an airplane, set against a backdrop of clouds and a sunset sky. The atmosphere is mysterious and intriguing, with a sense of wonder and curiosity.

frames.caption: A child and an adult are seated inside an airplane, gazing out the window at a mysterious flying object. The object resembles a classic UFO with bright lights around its edge, hovering outside the plane. The scene is bathed in warm, golden light from the setting sun.
frames.description: Inside an airplane cabin, a child and an adult are captivated by an unusual sight outside their window. A UFO-like object is visible, adding an element of mystery and intrigue to the otherwise serene flight.
